<h1 id="make-one-frame">make one frame</h1>
<p>years = range(1880,2011)
pieces = []
columns = [‚Äúname‚Äù, ‚Äúsex‚Äù, ‚Äúbirths‚Äù]</p>

<p>for year in years:
    path = ‚Äúc:\work\yob%d.txt‚Äù % year
    frame = pd.read_csv(path, names = columns)
    frame[‚Äúyear‚Äù] = year
    pieces.append(frame)
    names = pd.concat(pieces, ignore_index=True)</p>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>
- Summary
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>total_births = names.pivot_table(‚Äúbirths‚Äù, index = ‚Äòyear‚Äô, columns=‚Äôsex‚Äô, aggfunc=sum)</p>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>- Plot
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>total_births.plot(title=‚ÄùÎÖÑÎèÑÎ≥Ñ ÏÑ±Î≥Ñ Ï∂úÏÉù Ïà´Ïûê‚Äù)
```</p>

